Roach 2 U-Boot environment variable print/set (uconfig)
-------------------------------------------------------

The uconfig application can print/set roach 2 u-boot
environment variables from flash.

NOTE: This application is similar to /u-boot/tools/env/.

Dependencies
1. katcp library
    https://casper.berkeley.edu/wiki/KATCP
    https://github.com/ska-sa/katcp_devel
